<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Chanchinpha Chieh Zelin</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Sepgim lungkham buoina kinawk laka hin,
 I Lalpa Pathien in ei pui zel;
 Pa thutiem Ni lopi chu a hungtung tai,
 Saltangte pawtdawkna ni lopi.

[V2]
 Chanchinpha deihum chieh zel inla,
 Gamthim dang a saltangte pui di'n.

[V3]
 2. Ma a pilehpu te'n zie ni lopi hi,
 Mu nuomin ana thil zing mahleu;
 Mulo in thangvan sang a kaizo tau ie,
 Van zawhna lopi chu chang dingin.

[V4]
 3. Aw damna, damna Gospel lengviel inla,
 Kawl kimvel tiengin va leng inla;
 Gimtheite nawpna, vakvaite di'n In nuom,
 Na pak gimlim namtin damna din.

[V5]
 4. Aw nam chengcheng leh thilsiem tin cheng tenle,
 Lalpa lopi pakcha'n Aw suoh un;
 Kalvari hehpihna mak tak mai ziek in,
 Ei uh di'n damna lui a luong tai.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>309</hymn_number>
</song>